08:46.120 --> 08:47.720
And you can write to me if there's a problem

08:47.720 --> 08:50.920
and we can reschedule, et cetera.

08:50.920 --> 08:53.600
So you see that there's a different way

08:53.600 --> 08:56.840
one engages with even the logistical level

08:56.840 --> 08:59.440
of handling an analysis.

08:59.480 --> 09:02.320
So this manifests itself on all the other levels.

09:02.320 --> 09:05.400
So what I'm saying, when I'm saying that autism

09:05.400 --> 09:08.840
is a distinct mode of being, is I'm

09:08.840 --> 09:13.800
saying that one needs to handle an analysis under the hypothesis

09:13.800 --> 09:17.160
of autism in a way that is different than the one

09:17.160 --> 09:24.000
that we would do when there is a hypothesis of psychosis,

09:24.000 --> 09:25.760
perversion, and neurosis.

